  "body": "I've found I can get children's refs in ReactTransitionGroup. Just like\r\n\r\n```\r\n<TransitionGroup ref={(ref) => this._refs = ref}>\r\n    <div>Hello</div>\r\n</TransitionGroup>\r\n```\r\n\r\nThen I can get ```<div>Hello</div>``` by ```this._refs.refs['.$.0']```\r\n\r\nIt's quite ugly. \r\n\r\nIs there any better way?",
